EXAMPLES OF HUMAN RIGHTS VIOLATIONS DURING INTERNET SHUTDOWNS:
#InternetShutdowns & #humanrights violations go hand in hand as they restrict the ability of important human rights activities to be organised and conducted. https://t.co/Wxwbn5CGXn

THE ECONOMIC IMPACT OF INTERNET SHUTDOWNS:
According to @top10vpn, internet shutdowns around the world grew by +36% to over 30,000 hours in 2021, costing the global economy $5.45 billion.
https://t.co/ncCmSkGvXi

THE STATE OF INTERNET SHUTDOWNS IN 2021:
According to @accessnow, there were more than 50 #internetshutdowns in the first five months of 21â€™.
Even though there were fewer shutdowns than in previous years, the length of many was longer.
https://t.co/TyMayHNYNA

#InternetShutdowns are often accompanied by heightened state repression, military offensives, and violence. Shutdowns violate #humanrights, severely disrupt peopleâ€™s lives and livelihoods, and have a global economic impact.
#advocacyassembly

WHEN DO THEY HAPPEN:
#InternetDisruptions & #shutdowns often happen during #protests, elections, and periods of political instability. Governments often try to justify shutdowns by saying they are being implemented for â€œpublic safetyâ€
#advocacyassembly #internetshutdowns https://t.co/ZawrwMkFnu

FORMS OF INTERNET SHUTDOWNS:
An #internetshutdown can happen because the speed of the internet is disrupted, or throttled, â€“ so you can still access the #internet, but itâ€™s deliberately made so slow so you canâ€™t upload a video or an image.
#advocacyassembly https://t.co/dkWocDehxH

INTERNET SHUTDOWN: DEFINITION
An #internetshutdown is â€œan intentional disruption of internet or electronic communications of more than an hourâ€. Other names of shutdowns are #blackouts, #killswitches, #networkdisruptions & #internetoutage https://t.co/OGGTS4af3g
